-- China Construction Bank, AVIC Start $2.95 Billion Aviation-Industry Fund
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-07T03:01:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-07/china-construction-bank-avic-start-2-95-billion-aviation-industry-fund.html

          
          
             China Construction Bank Corp. and
China Aviation Industry Corp. started a fund to boost the
country’s aviation industry, according to a statement posted on
the lender’s website today.  
 The fund, which plans to raise as much as 5 billion yuan in
the first phase, aims to boost capital to 20 billion yuan
eventually, according to the statement.  
